All 25 blasts strike Gemini Dragon as it flys away, parks flying from 
the wounds. However hope for it is in sight as it spys the coast and 
then demerges. Both Gemini 1 and Gemini 2 press a button on their 
wrist making the two orbs from before rise from the ocean and fly to 
them which they enter...

Meanwhile, Vampiza fires a blast of chaochitan energy at Windlord.
